narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This seminar aided us in two areas of scholarly growth: 1) how to advance clear interpretations of texts, and 2) how to verbally present our arguments.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: In one of our last class sessions, we discussed making the expectations for seminar discussions more explicit to students in the first few meetings. I think this might help class discussion to move in ways which are generative for everyone present.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. Nancy provided texts for us which helped us to think through core topics in our field (as well as texts which asked for interpretative work which is essential in our field).
